00:00:33.939 --> 00:00:35.320
What is really going on?

00:00:36.380 --> 00:00:39.200
Everything is under my control.

00:00:39.479 --> 00:00:42.560
Chen Yuanqi, you do have some skill.

00:00:43.219 --> 00:00:45.679
But you're just a pawn on my chessboard.

00:00:46.219 --> 00:00:47.740
My cultivation has been restored.

00:00:48.200 --> 00:00:51.520
Tell me, who truly rules this world?

00:00:53.320 --> 00:00:54.200
Chen Yuanqi.

00:00:54.740 --> 00:00:56.479
I told you I'd make you regret it.

00:00:56.600 --> 00:00:59.240
Dreaming of defying fate? Impossible.

00:01:00.579 --> 00:01:02.039
I gave you a chance.

00:01:02.920 --> 00:01:06.040
All I ever wanted was to climb up the social ladder.

00:01:06.599 --> 00:01:08.319
But the Fu family cast me aside like trash.

00:01:09.260 --> 00:01:11.299
Only the cult leader saw my worth.

00:01:11.879 --> 00:01:14.099
He'll make me the Demon Queen once it's done.

00:01:14.819 --> 00:01:16.879
That's the status I deserve.

00:01:18.480 --> 00:01:20.959
You're all surrounded by me alone.

00:01:21.719 --> 00:01:23.260
Surrender and you'll be spared.

00:01:23.640 --> 00:01:27.719
Otherwise, today is your day to die.

00:01:35.400 --> 00:01:36.900
Qingyun, Qingyun!

00:01:37.579 --> 00:01:39.760
Don't become a lackey of Dugu Zhantian.

00:01:40.019 --> 00:01:41.640
Sinners against the Righteous Path.

00:01:42.599 --> 00:01:44.120
Enemies of the Righteous Path.

00:01:45.180 --> 00:01:48.359
If the Righteous Path abandons me, I'd rather become a demon.

00:01:51.739 --> 00:01:52.459
Stop!

00:01:54.859 --> 00:01:56.260
